IntelliJ IDEA has lots of configuration options in the IDE preferences. Come up with several ideas for improving the Settings search feature.

For one of your ideas, formulate the tasks required for designers and developers to implement it.

Come up with the metrics that you will use to evaluate the success of the implemented improvement.


